  "body": "while running the validator client on pyrmont, things have been smooth, for the most part, but every now and then i'll see a timeout from one of the requests.  for example: \r\n\r\n```\r\n2021-01-29 18:03:25 []              verbose: HttpClient POST error url=/beacon_committee_subscriptions message=timeout of 4000ms exceeded\r\n    Error: timeout of 4000ms exceeded\r\n        at createError (/home/seraph/work/ChainSafe/lodestar/node_modules/axios/lib/core/createError.js:16:15)\r\n        at RedirectableRequest.handleRequestTimeout (/home/seraph/work/ChainSafe/lodestar/node_modules/axios/lib/adapters/http.js:280:16)\r\n        at Object.onceWrapper (events.js:297:20)\r\n        at RedirectableRequest.emit (events.js:209:13)\r\n        at RedirectableRequest.EventEmitter.emit (domain.js:476:20)\r\n        at Timeout._onTimeout (/home/seraph/work/ChainSafe/lodestar/node_modules/follow-redirects/index.js:166:13)\r\n        at listOnTimeout (internal/timers.js:531:17)\r\n        at processTimers (internal/timers.js:475:7)\r\n```\r\n\r\nI also see this same error in other areas of the code too, which will sometimes cause us to miss attestations:\r\n```\r\n2021-01-29 18:28:43 []              verbose: HttpClient GET error url=/aggregate_attestation?attestation_data_root=0xf85f73e0430207c7cd8009f6fd87b0d416df0ff98ec709b42b6368dc15354281&slot=522142 message=timeout of 4000ms exceeded\r\n    Error: timeout of 4000ms exceeded\r\n        at createError (/home/seraph/work/ChainSafe/lodestar/node_modules/axios/lib/core/createError.js:16:15)\r\n        at RedirectableRequest.handleRequestTimeout (/home/seraph/work/ChainSafe/lodestar/node_modules/axios/lib/adapters/http.js:280:16)\r\n        at Object.onceWrapper (events.js:297:20)\r\n        at RedirectableRequest.emit (events.js:209:13)\r\n        at RedirectableRequest.EventEmitter.emit (domain.js:476:20)\r\n        at Timeout._onTimeout (/home/seraph/work/ChainSafe/lodestar/node_modules/follow-redirects/index.js:166:13)\r\n        at listOnTimeout (internal/timers.js:531:17)\r\n        at processTimers (internal/timers.js:475:7)\r\n```\r\n\r\nEither our timeout is too soon, or maybe something else is going on.",
